=\"10\"]','Training','','inherit','open','open','','19-autosave','','','2012-12-04 11:15:03','2012-12-04 09:15:03','',19,'http://swordschool.com/?p=25',0,'revision','',0),(26,1,'2012-09-17 21:05:25','2012-09-17 19:05:25','Content for current students','Current Students','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-3','','','2012-09-17 21:05:25','2012-09-17 19:05:25','',19,'http://swordschool.com/?p=26',0,'revision','',0),(27,1,'2012-09-17 21:22:53','2012-09-17 19:22:53','<div>\r\n<pre>[google-calendar-events id=\"1\" type=\"ajax\" title=\"here are some events\" max=\"100\"]</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nContent for current students','Current Students','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-4','','','2012-09-17 21:22:53','2012-09-17 19:22:53','',19,'http://swordschool.com/?p=27',0,'revision','',0),(28,1,'2012-09-17 21:32:10','2012-09-17 19:32:10','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://swordschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/SEShelsinki1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-367\" title=\"SEShelsinki\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://swordschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/SEShelsinki1-1024x634.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"634\" /></a>\r\n<h4>Location</h4>\r\nThe School\'s Salle is at Luiskatie 8, 00770 Helsinki, a 25 min ride on the 77 bus from Rautatientori. The entrance is around the back of the building.\r\n<h4>Beginners\' Course</h4>\r\nThe next Medieval Combat beginners\' course will run on Tuesday evenings from February 25th to April 15th. <a title=\"Helsinki Beginners\" href=\"http://swordschool.net/index.php/helsinki-beginners/\">Click here for more information about the course content.</a>\r\n<h3>Helsinki schedule</h3>\r\nOver the Christmas period: class will run as normal on the 19th December, the 30th December, and from January 2nd onwards. We are closed on December 23rd, 24th, 26th, and 31st. If a free scholar chooses to run extra training during this time, it will be announced on <a title=\"SES FB group\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/6336234189/\" target=\"_blank\">our Facebook group</a> page.\r\n<div>\r\n<pre>[timetable id=1 start=\"today\"]</pre>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\nTuesday evening Basic classes will be mostly taught by Class Leaders and those working towards that qualification, usually under the direction of the Instructor. This is to provide opportunities for senior students who wish to teach to learn to do so.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Payments</b>\r\n\r\nPayments to the Suomen Historiallisen Miekkailun Seura Ry should go to this account:\r\n\r\nNordea FI53 1015 3000 2149 03\r\n\r\nPlease remember to use your viitenumero, or explain in the message field what it is for.\r\n\r\nIf in any doubt, please ask the treasurer: laura dot husu at gmail dot com\r\n<h3>Classes and Events calendar</h3>\r\n<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=0n7svv9vc85991i4kntp373vu0%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;ctz=Europe/Helsinki\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\"></iframe>','Helsinki','','publish','closed','open','','helsinki','','','2013-12-13 11:13:54','2013-12-13 09:13:54','',19,'http://swordschool.com/?page_id=28',0,'page','',1),(29,1,'2012-09-17 21:31:59','2012-09-17 19:31:59','','Helsinki','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-v1','','','2012-09-17 21:31:59','2012-09-17 19:31:59','',28,'http://swordschool.com/?p=29',0,'revision','',0),(30,1,'2012-09-17 21:32:10','2012-09-17 19:32:10','Helsinki branch','Helsink','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-v1','','','2012-09-17 21:32:10','2012-09-17 19:32:10','',28,'http://swordschool.com/?p=30',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2012-09-17 21:32:58','2012-09-17 19:32:58','Our Jyväskylä branch webpage: http://www.historiallinenmiekkailu.com','Jyväskylä','','publish','closed','open','','jyvaskyla','','','2012-11-29 14:42:19','2012-11-29 12:42:19','',19,'http://swordschool.com/?page_id=31',0,'page','',0),(32,1,'2012-09-17 21:32:44','2012-09-17 19:32:44','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','31-revision','','','2012-09-17 21:32:44','20