t.</a>\n<h3>Helsinki schedule</h3>\nIf a free scholar chooses to run extra training, it will be added to the calendar below, and when possible also on <a title=\"SES FB group\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/6336234189/\" target=\"_blank\">our Facebook group</a> page.\n<div>\n<pre>[timetable id=1 start=\"today\"]</pre>\n<h3></h3>\nTuesday evening Basic classes will be mostly taught by Class Leaders and those working towards that qualification, usually under the direction of the Instructor. This is to provide opportunities for senior students who wish to teach to learn to do so.\n\n</div>\n<b>Payments</b>\n\nPayments to the Suomen Historiallisen Miekkailun Seura Ry should go to this account:\n\nNordea FI53 1015 3000 2149 03\n\nPlease remember to use your viitenumero, or explain in the message field what it is for.\n\nIf in any doubt, please ask the treasurer: laura dot husu at gmail dot com\n<h3>Classes and Events calendar</h3>\n<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=0n7svv9vc85991i4kntp373vu0%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;ctz=Europe/Helsinki\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\"></iframe>','Helsinki','','inherit','open','open','','28-autosave-v1','','','2014-01-22 11:53:49','2014-01-22 09:53:49','',28,'http://swordschool.com/?p=58',0,'revision','',0),(59,1,'2012-09-17 21:32:15','2012-09-17 19:32:15','Helsinki branch','Helsinki','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-v1','','','2012-09-17 21:32:15','2012-09-17 19:32:15','',28,'http://swordschool.com/?p=59',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2012-09-25 22:42:42','2012-09-25 20:42:42','<pre>[menu name=\"branches\"]</pre>\r\n<pre>[timetable id=1 start=\"today\"]\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec purus arcu, volutpat elementum pharetra sed, sollicitudin ultricies ipsum. Nam malesuada ante quam, a bibendum dolor. Sed varius tellus sed purus facilisis sed lobortis velit scelerisque. Ut elementum ultrices porta. Pellentesque semper nisl et tel