of the building.\r\n<h4>Beginners\' Course</h4>\r\nThe next beginners\' course on medieval combat in Helsinki will run on Tuesday evenings in October, exact dates to be confirmed. <a title=\"Helsinki Beginners\" href=\"http://swordschool.net/index.php/helsinki-beginners/\">Click here for more information about the course content.</a> We are also planning a beginners\' course on the rapier, to start in August, but that is not yet fixed.\r\n<h3>Helsinki schedule</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre>[timetable id=1 start=\"today\"]</pre>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\nTuesday evening Basic classes will be mostly taught by Class Leaders and those working towards that qualification, usually under the direction of the Instructor. This is to provide opportunities for senior students who wish to teach to learn to do so.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Payments</b>\r\n\r\nPayments to the Suomen Historiallisen Miekkailun Seura Ry should go to this account:\r\n\r\nNordea FI53 1015 3000 2149 03\r\n\r\nPlease remember to use your viitenumero, or explain in the message field what it is for.\r\n\r\nIf in any doubt, please ask the treasurer: laura dot husu at gmail dot com\r\n<h3>Classes and Events calendar</h3>\r\n<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=0n7svv9vc85991i4kntp373vu0%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;ctz=Europe/Helsinki\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\"></iframe>','Helsinki','','inherit','closed','open','','28-revision-v1','','','2013-05-21 08:57:21','2013-05-21 06:57:21','',28,'http://swordschool.com/index.php/28-revision-26/',0,'revision','',0),(316,3,'2013-05-22 13:53:57','2013-05-22 11:53:57','Chris Chatfield, co-founder of <a title=\"1595\" href=\"http://www.the1595.com\" target=\"_blank\">the 1595 Club</a>, and now a full-time instructor, will take us through his radical interpretation of Vincentio Saviolo\'s swordsmanship style. Saviolo wrote his treatise in 1595, and was an arch-enemy of George Silver.\r\nThe seminar will be based on Saviolo\'s sword form, but extrapola